Dialogue: 0,00:18:58.33,00:19:00.23,JP-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}その実ブルーなので
Dialogue: 0,00:19:00.34,00:19:02.85,JP-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}困っちゃうよ　目立っちゃうな
Dialogue: 0,00:19:02.96,00:19:05.23,JP-BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\3c&H0F7FDC&\fad(200,200)}散々だなぁ　逃げたいなぁ
